data.name: deb_pause_info_lbl.ToolTip
data.value:
The Ika SPT Launcher shuts down 5 seconds after a successful run. Check this if you want the application to wait for user input before closing if there are applications that are not found by the launcher.
DEFAULT: No/Unchecked

data.name: ea_section_info_lbl.ToolTip
data.value:
Applications to start along with SPT Launcher and/or Server. You can also select if you want them to start minimized or not.
Launch Order: - Server (if local) - Launcher - Applications in the list from top to bottom
DEFAULT: None
